%A0which%20first%20reported%20the%20news%2C%20that%20other%20executives%20had%20helped%20to%20fill%20the%20role%20in%20the%20two%20years%20since%20Musk%20bought%20the%20platform%20for%20%2444%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20X%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22220e3692-5d72-4976-8a08-c7db2b99abb8%5C%22%3EPresidential%20pardon%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBanki%20received%20a%20pardon%20from%20President%20Trump%20on%20January%2019%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20pardoned%20for%20a%20case%20connected%20to%202010%20charges%20of%20making%20false%20statements.%20He%20also%20faced%20charges%20related%20to%20sanctions%20violations%20against%20Iran%2C%20which%20were%20later%20overturned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBanki%20spent%20almost%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20before%20he%20was%20released%20in%20November%202011%20following%20a%20successful%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20following%20the%20pardon%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%202010%2C%20Dr.%20Banki%20was%20charged%20with%20monetary%20violations%20of%20Iranian%20sanctions%20and%20making%20false%20statements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20felony%20charges%20for%20making%20false%20statements%20have%20prevented%20Dr.%20Banki%20from%20resuming%20a%20full%20life.%20In%20the%20years%20since%20his%20conviction%2C%20Dr.%20Banki%20has%20dedicated%20himself%20to%20his%20community%20and%20maintained%20a%20sincere%20love%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrumpwhitehouse.archives.gov%2Fbriefings-statements%2Fstatement-press-secretary-regarding-executive-grants-clemency-012021%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouse%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBanki%20was%20among%2073%20individuals%20who%20were%20granted%20pardons%20in%20the%20final%20days%20of%20Trump's%20administration.%20An%20additional%2070%20individuals%20also%20had%20their%20sentences%20commuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBanki's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frezastory.com%2Fpardon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20states%20he%20left%20postwar%20Iran%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%201990s%20and%20traveled%20to%20the%20US%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20American%20dream%20and%20to%20have%20a%20shot%20at%20a%20better%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20website%20adds%20that%20he%20graduated%20from%20UC%20Berkeley%20with%20a%20double%20major%20and%20Princeton%20with%20a%20Ph.D.%20before%20joining%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20in%20New%20York%20City%20in%202005.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20presidential%20pardon%2C%20his%20website%20states%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EJoy%20at%20the%20outcome.%20Relief%20for%20justice%20at%20last.%20Sadness%20of%20the%20utter%20pain%2C%20distress%2C%20and%20hopelessness%20throughout.%20Exhaustion%20of%20the%20journey.%20And%20ultimately%20thankful%20to%20have%20a%20grave%20weight%20off%20my%20shoulders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22032f3435-2fc6-4b2b-ad49-f75165f8fbad%5C%22%3EX's%20financial%20issues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBanki%20is%20joining%20the%20X%20at%20a%20critical%20time%20for%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Musk%20took%20control%20of%20the%20platform%20in%202022%2C%20the%20company%20has%20faced%20financial%20challenges%2C%20including%20a%20drop%20in%20advertising%20revenue.%20Some%20major%20brands%20have%20pulled%20their%20content%20from%20X%2C%20and%20the%20platform%20has%20struggled%20to%20win%20back%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20September%20report%2C%20market%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-advertisers-plan-to-pull-back-spending-survey-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5