24-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20classroom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20think%20educators%20will%20increasingly%20learn%20how%20to%20adapt%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298cf080d-f532-456b-9116-3954f62b8133%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20playing%20around%20with%20ChatGPT%20and%20wanted%20to%20use%20it%20in%20class%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20experimented%20with%20ChatGPT%20over%20the%20holidays.%20I%20fed%20it%20essay%20prompts%20and%20saw%20it%20was%20able%20to%20generate%20arguments%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20it%20was%20making%20basic%20mistakes.%20I%20gave%20it%20a%20prompt%20about%20the%20Shakespeare%20play%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EMuch%20Ado%20About%20Nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20produced%20quotes%20from%20%26quot%3BAs%20You%20Like%20It.%26quot%3B%20But%20I%20knew%20the%20technology%20would%20improve.%20I%20began%20to%20despair%2C%20thinking%20I'd%20have%20to%20reinvent%20myself%20as%20a%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20I%20tried%20planning%20lessons%20and%20generating%20worksheets%20with%20ChatGPT%2C%20I%20saw%20how%20helpful%20it%20could%20be.%20I%20was%20having%20fun%20and%20wanted%20to%20help%20my%20students%20use%20it%20as%20a%20tool%20instead%20of%20to%20cheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20considered%20how%20to%20suggest%20uses%20for%20ChatGPT%20where%20students%20could%20still%20demonstrate%20their%20critical%20thinking%20skills.%20When%20I%20got%20back%20to%20school%2C%20I%20talked%20to%20the%20school's%20administrators%20and%20the%20tech%20specialist%2C%20asking%20permission%20to%20test%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-tools-replace-teachers-high-school-students-learning-education-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20in%20the%20classroom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20starting%20with%20my%2012th-grade%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ee9405b-2549-4b9b-a5ec-4e5699b79d02%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELetting%20students%20use%20AI%20as%20a%20tool%20has%20been%20more%20helpful%20than%20trying%20to%20catch%20cheating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20by%20walking%20students%20through%20experiments%20I'd%20done%20with%20ChatGPT.%20One%20activity%20involved%20getting%20them%20to%20write%20an%20introductory%20paragraph.%20I'd%20feed%20those%20paragraphs%20into%20AI%2C%20asking%20it%20to%20write%20an%20essay%20based%20on%20the%20introduction.%20Then%2C%20I'd%20ask%20students%20to%20edit%20and%20critique%20what%20the%20AI%20was%20capable%20of%20compared%20to%20their%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20around%20January%202023%2C%20and%20my%20students%20were%20disappointed%20in%20the%20product.%20They%20felt%20the%20arguments%20it%20made%20were%20repetitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20my%20students%20mostly%20use%20AI%20for%20editing.%20Once%20they've%20finished%20an%20essay%2C%20they'll%20run%20it%20through%20AI%20editing%20software%20to%20clean%20up%20sentence%20structure%20and%20ensure%20their%20tenses%20are%20aligned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20told%20the%20students%20I%20won't%20be%20checking%20for%20AI%20in%20their%20work.%20I've%20tried%20using%20programs%20that%20claim%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-detection-tool-false-positives-student-writing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetect%20AI%20writing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20produce%20false%20positives%20and%20negatives.%20I%20tested%20something%20I%20wrote%20myself%2C%20and%20the%20detector%20told%20me%20it%20was%2070%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-denied-requests-generate-images-candidates-election-trump-harris-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-generated%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20good%20chance%20students%20are%20getting%20away%20with%20using%20more%20AI%20than%20I%20want%20them%20to%2C%20but%20those%20who%20want%20to%20circumvent%20systems%20would%20have%20done%20so%20without%20AI%2C%20such%20as%20by%20having%20their%20big%20sisters%20in%20college%20help%20to%20write%20their%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20that%20students%20have%20embraced%20my%20message%20and%20understand%20AI%20can%20only%20take%20you%20so%20far.%20I've%20set%20assignments%20where%20they%20have%20to%20do%20their%20own%20thesis-creation%20and%20research%20prior%20to%20using%20the%20tools%2C%20and%20they%20seem%20to%20appreciate%20that%20combination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20some%20students%20feel%20less%20overwhelmed%20by%20longer%20writing%20assignments%20because%20they%20have%20a%20tool%20to%20help%20them.%20But%20I've%20seen%20other%20students%20use%20AI%20to%20their%20detriment%20by%20getting%20it%20to%20write%20their%20work%20and%20not%20editing%20it%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20fellow%20teacher%20had%20a%20number%20of%20students%20use%20AI%20on%20an%20assignment%20without%20permission.%20I%20suggested%20that%20she%20speak%20with%20each%20student%20to%20see%20if%20they%20could%20explain%20their%20work.%20Some%20had%20actually%20learned%20the%20information%20and%20were%20able%20to%20explain%20their%20essays%20in%20depth%2C%20while%20others%20failed%20at%20that%20task%2C%20and%20she%20asked%20them%20to%20redo%20the%20assignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20making%20sure%20students%20are%20really%20learning.%20One%20way%20I%20assess%20their%20skills%20is%20by%20assigning%20handwritten%20in-class%20essays%20and%20take-home%20essays%20where%20they%20can%20access%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226125a0fb-5148-43c2-a94b-a754f245f982%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'd%20guess%20that%20AI%20tools%20will%20be%20used%20more%20widely%20by%20teachers%20in%20the%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20received%20negative%20feedback%20from%20a%20parent%20about%20my%20methods.%20At%20our%20school%2C%20some%20teachers%20are%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-use-chatgpt-daily-life-work-save-ti