riety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fjimmy-kimmel-trump-matt-gaetz-attorney-general-sex-trafficking-special-skills-1236209948%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Takes%20Job%20Exam%20Decision%20Amid%20Prayagraj%20Protest%2C%20Students%20Say%20Not%20Enough%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20growing%20political%20row%20over%20the%20students'%20protest%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20today%20decided%20to%20hold%20a%20key%20recruitment%20exam%20in%20a%20single%20shift.%20While%20the%20prelims%20for%20the%20Provincial%20Civil%20Service%20(PCS)%20exam%20will%20be%20held%20in%20one%20day%2C%20the%20commission%20has%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20how%20the%20exam%20to%20recruit%20review%20officers%20and%20assistant%20review%20officers%20can%20be%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%2C%20however%2C%20failed%20to%20pacify%20the%20protesting%20students.%20The%20protesters%20have%20accused%20the%20state%20service%20commission%20of%20trying%20to%20break%20up%20the%20agitation.%20They%20have%20said%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20protest%20till%20the%20government%20decides%20to%20hold%20the%20exam%20for%20RO%2FARO%20posts%20in%20a%20single%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20commission's%20earlier%20announcement%20that%20the%20two%20job%20exams%20would%20be%20held%20in%20two%20shifts%20over%20two%20days.%20They%20have%20demanded%20%26quot%3Bone%20day%2C%20one%20shift%26quot%3B%20exams%20as%20they%20fear%20multiple%20dates%20and%20shifts%20will%20raise%20the%20risk%20of%20paper%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20hold%20exams%20in%20shifts%20was%20taken%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20applicants%20and%20to%20uphold%20the%20exam's%20sanctity.%20A%20spokesperson%20had%20said%20they%20would%20hold%20exams%20only%20at%20centres%20where%20possibility%20of%20irregularities%20is%20eliminated.%20The%20spokesperson%20had%20said%20that%20only%20government%20or%20funded%20educational%20institutions%20within%20a%2010-km%20radius%20of%20a%20bus%20stand%2C%20railway%20station%20or%20treasury%2C%20and%20with%20no%20history%20of%20suspicion%20or%20blacklisting%20are%20being%20designated%20as%20examination%20centres.%20It%20is%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20the%20commission%20had%20to%20opt%20for%20exams%20in%20shifts%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20had%20also%20said%20that%20a%20normalisation%20process%20will%20be%20used%20to%20evaluate%20the%20results%20because%20the%20exams%20are%20being%20held%20across%20multiple%20days%20or%20shifts.%20This%2C%20the%20panel%20said%2C%20was%20commonly%20used%20across%20the%20country%20and%20is%20supported%20by%20several%20court%20rulings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20students%20were%20not%20convinced%20and%20stepped%20up%20their%20agitation%2C%20leading%20to%20chaotic%20scenes%20outside%20the%20state%20commission's%20office%20in%20Prayagraj.%20Top%20officials%20of%20the%20commission%20met%20today%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20and%20came%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20announcement.%20The%20decision%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20was%20taken%20after%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20have%20rejected%20this%20solution.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20misleading%20us.%20We%20are%20not%20moving%20from%20here%20till%20they%20announce%20that%20RO%2FARO%20exam%20will%20also%20be%20held%20in%20one%20day%2C%20one%20shift.%20We%20have%20two%20demands%2C%20they%20have%20fulfilled%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20protester.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20also%20said%20that%20it%20is%20only%20a%20verbal%20announcement%20so%20far%20and%20they%20won't%20stop%20the%20protest%20till%20an%20official%20notification%20for%20both%20exams%20is%20put%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20both%20exams%20in%20a%20a%20single%20shift.%20Why%20are%20you%20setting%20up%20a%20committee%3F%20They%20basically%20want%20the%20protesters%20to%20go%20away.%20They%20want%20to%20weaken%20the%20agitation%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20moving%20from%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20protester%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20protester%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20talk%20of%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20and%20they%20can't%20even%20hold%20an%20exam%20for%2010%20lakh%20students%20in%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Another%20protester%20said%20the%20latest%20announcement%20was%20part%20of%20a%20'divide%20and%20rule'%20plan.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20separate%20PCS%20and%20RO%2FARO.%20No%20one%20will%20go%20from%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20protesters%20started%20criticising%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20others%20said%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20drag%20party%20politics%20in%20their%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Political%20Backdrop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20commission's%20decision%20amid%20the%20massive%20protest%20comes%20against%20a%20political%20backdrop.%20Nine%20Assembly%20constituencies%20of%20the%20state%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20November%2020%20bypolls%20and%20the%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20corner%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20over%20the%20Prayagraj%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bheartless%26quot%3B%20state%20government%20should%20accept%20the%20fair%20demands%20of%20the%20students%2C%20if%20only%20out%20of%20political%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission's%20attitude%20was%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binsensitive%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20the%20students%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20the%20BJP%20government's%20inefficiency%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20tackle%20this%20agitation%20before%20it%20gets%20out%20of%20hand.%20Earlier%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20called%20for%20an%20amicable%20solution.%20%26quot%3BAll%20competent%20officials%20should%20listen%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20students%20sensitively%20and%20find%20a%20quick%20solution.%20Ensure%20that%20the%20precious%20time%20of%20the%20students%20is%20not%20spent%20in%20agitation%20but%20in%20their%20preparation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731583920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fv7ic8icg_up-protest_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-rolls-back-decision-on-prayagraj-job-exam-after-massive-protests-by-students-7018167%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20growing%20political%20row%20over%20the%20students'%20protest%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20today%20decided%20to%20hold%20a%20key%20recruitment%20exam%20in%20a%20single%20shift%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Councillor%20Resigns%20Amid%20Chaos%20Ahead%20Of%20Delhi%20Mayor%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChaos%20overtook%20the%20mayoral%20election%20in%20Delhi%20today%20as%20the%20Congress%20boycotted%20the%20poll%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20new%20Mayor-who%20would%20be%20a%20Dalit%20--%20%C2%A0serve%20a%20full%20term.%20The%20election%2C%20normally%20held%20every%20April%2C%20has%20been%20delayed%20over%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20new%20Mayor%20is%20expected%20to%20get%20only%20a%20five-month%20term.%20Amid%20the%20chaos%2C%20Congress's%20Mohammad%20Khushnood%20and%20his%20wife%20Sabila%20Begum%20--%20Councillor%20of%20Mustafabad%20Ward%20243)%20--%20resigned%20from%20the%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20party%2C%20saying%20she%20would%20vote%20for%20the%20AAP%20candidate.%20While%20the%20seven%20Congress%20members%20walked%20out%20as%20the%20voting%20started%2C%20she%20stayed%20back%20to%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20resignation%20letter%2C%20Sabila%20Begum%20said%20her%20objection%20was%20to%20the%20party's%20walkout%20decision%2C%20which%20would%20only%20benefit%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20election%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20standing%20committee%20was%20to%20be%20held.%20In%20that%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20councillors%20were%20given%20the%20order%20to%20walk%20out%2C%20the%20result%20of%20which%20was%20that%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20won%20and%20the%20BJP%20captured%20the%20standing%20committee.%20In%20the%20last%20mayor%20election%20also%20we%20had%20walked%20out%20on%20the%20order%20of%20the%20party%2C%20due%20to%20which%20we%20had%20to%20face%20the%20anger%20of%20our%20people%20in%20our%20ward%2C'%20her%20letter%20read.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20resign%20from%20the%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%20because%20the%20ward%20from%20which%20I%20am%20a%20Municipal%20Councillor%20is%20a%20Muslim%20dominated%20area%20and%20the%20people%20of%20the%20area%20cannot%20support%20the%20BJP%20in%20any%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20added.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20delay%20in%20the%20election%20took%20place%20as%20then%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20case.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThen%20AAP%20boycotted%20the%20election%20held%20in%20September%20after%20the%20councillors%20were%20frisked.%20That%20time%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20abstained%20from%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20further%20delay%20over%20procedural%20disputes%2C%20including%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20presiding%20officer%20by%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20term%20is%20meant%20for%20a%20candidate%20from%20a%20reserved%20category.%20The%20rules%20say%20the%20post%2C%20for%20which%20elections%20are%20held%20every%20year%2C%20have%20categories%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20The%20first%20year%20is%20reserved%20for%20women%2C%20the%20second%20is%20for%20open%20category%2C%20the%20third%20for%20the%20reserved%20category%2C%20and%20the%20last%20two%20again%20are%20open%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal's%20AAP%20has%20fielded%20Mahesh%20Khichi%2C%20councillor%20from%20Devnagar%2C%20for%20the%20mayor's%20post%2C%20who%20is%20up%20against%20the%20BJP's%20Kishan%20Lal.%20The%20fight%20for%20the%20Deputy%20Mayor%20post%20is%20between%20AAP's%20Ravinder%20Bharadwaj%2C%20councillor%20of%20Aman%20Vihar%20and%20Nita%20Bisht.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20mayoral%20election%20after%20the%20AAP%20ended%20the%20BJP's%2015-year%20run%20at%20the%20civic%20body%20in%20December%202022.%20AAP's%20Shelly%20Oberoi%20is%20the%20outgoing%20Mayor%20and%20her%20Deputy%20is%20Mohammed%20Iqbal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731583800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fc1u1rjig_municipal-corporation-of-delhi-mcd-generic_625x300_15_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-councillor-resigns-amid-chaos-ahead-of-delhi-mayor-polls-7018383%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chaos%20overtook%20the%20mayoral%20election%20in%20Delhi%20today%20as%20the%20Congress%20said%20it%20would%20boycott%20the%20poll%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20new%20Mayor%20serve%20a%20full%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-councillor-resigns-amid-chaos-ahead-of-delhi-mayor-polls-