ing%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20the%2012%20ICC%20Board%20meetings%20since%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20on%20Sunday%20had%20confirmed%20that%20it%20received%20an%20email%20from%20the%20ICC%20that%20India%20declined%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20not%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20since%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20strikes.%20The%20two%20teams%20compete%20against%20each%20other%20only%20in%20ICC%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICC%2C%20the%20game's%20global%20governing%20body%2C%20has%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20written%20confirmation%20from%20the%20BCCI%20for%20India's%20inability%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20has%20conveyed%20to%20the%20ICC%20that%20security%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20country%20which%20successfully%20hosted%20England%20and%20New%20Zealand%20recently%20and%20promised%20the%20same%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remained%20steadfast%20on%20its%20stand%20to%20not%20have%20the%20event%20in%20hybrid%20model%2C%20like%20the%20last%20year's%20Asia%20Cup%20when%20India's%20matches%20were%20held%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20PCB%20and%20was%20discussing%20the%20schedule%20with%20the%20participating%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20has%20learnt%20that%20the%20PCB%20is%20also%20not%20keen%20to%20host%20the%20tournament%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20not%20even%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20the%20launch%20event%20in%20Lahore%20has%20been%20pushed%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20being%20planned%20in%20Lahore%20as%20per%20ICC%20management's%20briefing%20to%20the%20ICC%20CEC%20and%20ICC%20Board%20on%2021st%20October%20in%20Dubai.%20But%20this%20has%20now%20been%20put%20on%20a%20hold%2C%20informed%20an%20ICC%20insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3