0they%20could%20do%20this%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20need%20to%20hear%20that%20%E2%80%94%20they%20weren't%20worried%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221eb7e748-8fb3-4587-9880-108cf0259496%5C%22%3EFour%20families%20were%20walking%20by%20the%20end%20of%20swim%20practice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20day%20of%20swim%20I%20finished%20work%20and%20headed%20to%20the%20pool.%20I%20held%20my%20breath%20as%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-family-living-in-netherlands-new-perspective-on-modesty-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20into%20the%20locker%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20breathed%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20when%20I%20saw%20both%20girls%20changed%20for%20swimming%20and%20having%20a%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20they%20walk%3F%26quot%3B%20another%20mom%20asked%20me%20at%20pickup.%20She%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20her%20two%20daughters%20could%20handle%20the%20walk%2C%20but%20soon%2C%20they%20were%20asking%20to%20walk%20with%20my%20kids.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20swim%20season%2C%20four%20sets%20of%20siblings%20were%20walking%20from%20school%20to%20practice.%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20if%20that%20happened%20because%20I%20was%20the%20one%20to%20break%20the%20ice%2C%20but%20it%20was%20really%20heartening%20to%20see%20more%20kids%20walking%20independently.%20The%20kids%20loved%20it%20so%20much%20that%20they%20chose%20walking%20over%20a%20ride%2C%20even%20on%20the%20coldest%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20so%20many%20fond%20memories%20from%20walking%20to%20and%20from%20school%2C%20whether%20chatting%20with%20the%20crossing%20guard%2C%20making%20up%20silly%20games%2C%20or%20just%20exploring%20with%20friends.%20Walking%20to%20swim%20gave%20my%20kids%2C%20and%20eventually%20their%20friends%2C%20the%20unsupervised%2C%20independent%20space%20to%20have%20similar%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20want%20them%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20opportunities%20just%20because%20I'm%20worried%20about%20what%20