0same%20question%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20need%20money%3F%20If%20you%20do%2C%20just%20let%20me%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he'd%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20thinking%20%E2%80%94%20or%20sometimes%20even%20looking%20at%20him%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20respond%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20good%2C%20don't%20worry.%26quot%3B%20But%20was%20I%20actually%20good%3F%20Nope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20bank%20account%20was%20draining%2C%20and%20I%20was%20cost-cutting%20on%20everything.%20I%20was%20anxious%20about%20making%20a%20sustainable%20income%2C%20which%20made%20my%20sleeping%20and%20eating%20schedules%20unhealthy.%20Still%2C%20I'd%20decided%20years%20prior%20that%20I%20would%20never%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-mom-financial-assistance-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eask%20my%20parents%20for%20financial%20support%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%20when%20my%20dad%20%E2%80%94%20a%20retired%20businessman%20who%20knew%20sustaining%20a%20business%20was%20tough%20%E2%80%94%20asked%20again%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20making%20enough%20money%3F%20If%20you%20need%20more%2C%20tell%20me%3B%20it's%20no%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20looked%20at%20him%2C%20smiled%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what%2C%20I'm%20good%20for%20now.%20But%20if%20I%20need%20more%2C%20I'll%20tell%20you.%26quot%3B%20I%20meant%20every%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20did%20I%20go%20from%20hating%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-child-benefits-financial-support-parents-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easking%20my%20parents%20for%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20being%20open%20to%20it%3F%20Well%2C%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20self-work%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20I%20certainly%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20for%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6d1eea4-d838-4a92-85cc-875b991d14f7%5C%22%3EI%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20independent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20have%20always%20had%20money%2C%20so%20my%20resistance%20to%20taking%20their%20help%20wasn't%20coming%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoarding-cash-financial-trauma-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraumatic%20financial%20past%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20feelings%20of%20scarcity.%20Still%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20independent%2C%20and%20responsible%20on%20my%20own.%20And%20it%20was%20just%20as%20important%20to%20me%20to%20be%20perceived%20that%20way%20by%20parents%2C%20relatives%2C%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-degree-rely-parents-financial-support-nyc-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20my%20master's%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20organizational%20psychology%20in%202020%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20myself%20working%20in%20career%20paths%20that%20traditionally%20follow.%20I%20took%20up%20odd%20jobs%2C%20like%20teaching%20English%20online%2C%20testing%20apps%2C%20writing%20resumes%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20that%20paid.%20At%2024%2C%20I%20started%20freelancing%20as%20a%20copywriter%2C%20but%20I%20was%20always%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20broke.%20As%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20saving%20and%20avoiding%20going%20into%20debt%20rather%20than%20doing%20things%20that%20might%20further%20my%20learning%20or%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20image%20of%20the%20self-made%2C%20perfect%20daughter%20who%20could%20take%20care%20of%20herself%20for%20two%20years.%20I%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20loop%20of%20making%20decisions%20that%20guarded%20my%20ego%20instead%20of%20taking%20risks%20that%20might%20boost%20my%20career%20and%20set%20me%20up%20for%20the%20future.%20Then%2C%20at%2026%2C%20after%20being%20exhausted%20from%20freelancing%2C%20I%20got%20a%20full-time%20job%20that%20offered%20a%20stable%20income%20and%20moved%20out%20of%20my%20parents'%20home.%20But%20it%20didn't%20feel%20satisfying%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20in%20April%202024%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20freelance%20again%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20things%20had%20to%20be%20different%20and%20less%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211f9d3ab-3438-464e-828f-48cc6f09fa2a%5C%22%3EI%20realized%20that%20refusing%20my%20parents'%20help%20was%20holding%20me%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20my%20friends%20had%20dabbled%20in%20different%20careers%20and%20relied%20on%20their%20parents%20for%20money%20until%20their%20late%2020s%2C%20figuring%20out%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20do%20and%20building%20up%20a%20solid%20set%20of%20skills.%20Not%20only%20did%20they%20seem%20happier%20than%20I%20was%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategies-earn-more-money-negotiate-raise-start-side-hustle-budgetnista-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20more%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20met%20with%20one%20of%20these%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20a%20psychologist%20who%20is%20also%20a%20sound%20healer.%20I%20asked%20her%20how%20she%20had%20been%20OK%20with%20asking%20her%20parents%20for%20money%20for%20years%20after%20completing%20her%20education.%20Didn't%20she%20want%20to%20be%20independent%20and%20make%20her%20own%20income%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20me%20that%20exploration%20was%20important%20and%20that%20money%20was%20never%20the%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20though%20it%20was%20the%20eventual%20outcome.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20focused%20on%20showing%20people%20I%20have%20money%20instead%20of%20developing%20my%20skills%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20discovered%20my%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-passive-income-strategies-build-wealth-earning-money-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincome%20streams%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20family%20had%20money%2C%20so%20I%20was%20free%20to%20take%20more%20chances%20and%20try%20new%20things%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20I%20found%20professions%20that%20I%20love%2C%20and%20money%20followed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20she%20had%20a%20financial%20safety%20net%20made%20her%20fearless.%20Whenever%20she%20wanted%2C%20she%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20found%20what%20made%20her%20happy%20(and%20yes%2C%20eventually%20able%20to%20support%20herself).%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20was%20making%20life%20difficult%20for%20myself%20by%20blocking%20out%20financial%20support%20when%20I%20needed%20it%20the%20most.%20Freelancing%20was%20a%20new%20skill%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20choosing%20to%20accept%20help%20while%20I%20sharpened%20it%2C%20I%20let%20my%20ego%20get%20in%20the%20way.%20And%20that%20was%20taking%20me%20nowhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22810e5f1a-5bd4-439c-848e-05f5076e8334%5C%22%3EJust%20knowing%20I%20had%20a%20financial%20safety%20net%20has%20helped%20me%20achieve%20my%20goals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20moment%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20had%20financial%20backup%20and%20that%20no%20matter%20how%20my%20career%20went%2C%20I%20was%20going%20to%20be%20fine%2C%20my%20relationship%20with%20money%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20not%20to%20make%20fear-%20or%20scarcity-based%20decisions%20with%20my%20money%20and%20instead%20to%20play%20the%20long-term%20game.%20I%20started%20by%20listing%20my%20personal%20and%20professional%20goals%20for%20the%20next%20six%20months%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistake-investing-money-instead-of-saving-it-2024-04%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvested%20my%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20these%20goals.%20I%20joined%20writing%20communities%2C%20which%20have%20given%20me%20access%20to%20mentorship%2C%20and%20I%20also%20allowed%20myself%20to%20take%20up%20projects%20that%20don't%20pay%20well%20but%20are%20learning%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20also%20allow%20myself%20to%20rest%20when%20I%20need%20it.%20Whereas%20taking%20a%20break%20would%20have%20made%20me%20anxious%20before%2C%20I%20know%20now%20that%20if%20I%20need%20money%2C%20I%20can%20always%20ask%20for%20help%20from%20my%20parents%20or%20move%20back%20in%20with%20them%20if%20that%20would%20be%20a%20workable%20solution.%20It%20hasn't%20come%20to%20that%2C%20however%3B%20I'm%20consistently%20onboarding%20new%20clients%2C%20and%20whether%20in%20large%20quantities%20or%20small%2C%20money%20has%20been%20showing%20up%20through%20freelancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20waiting%20on%20my%20payments%20from%20freelance%20projects%2C%20I%20let%20my%20parents%20pay%20for%20groceries%20or%20my%20monthly%20stack%20of%20books.%20I%20feel%20happier%20and%20lighter%20while%20spending%2C%20investing%2C%20and%20making%20money.%20I'm%20proud%20of%20the%20growth%20I've%20seen%20in%20my%20career%20%E2%80%94%20and%20my%20bank%20account.%20My%20newfound%20freedom%20with%20money%20is%20beautiful.%20And%20all%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20let%20go%20of%20my%20ego%20and%20image%20and%20say%20yes%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-financial-safety-net-money-independence-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731582182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6734c1755ec9bfa3d63dc55c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-financial-safety-net-money-independence-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20parents%20offered%20me%20money%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20independent.%20When%20I%20accepted%20that%20I%20had%20a%20financial%20safety%20net%2C%20I%20made%20progress%20in%20my%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kanishka%20Nangare)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-financial-safety-net-money-independence-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AFSPA%20Imposed%20In%20New%20Areas%20Of%20Manipur%20Amid%20Fresh%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20reimposed%20a%20law%20to%20protect%20security%20forces%20in%20hostile%20areas%20in%20several%20new%20locations%20in%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%20The%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act%20has%20been%20reimposed%20in%20six%20police%20station%20areas%20including%20Jiribam%2C%20where%2010%20suspected%20Kuki%20militants%20were%20shot%20dead%20in%20an%20encounter%20with%20the%20security%20forces%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20from%20where%20three%20women%20and%20three%20children%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20were%20kidnapped%20by%20suspected%20insurgents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AFSPA%20gives%20sweeping%20powers%20to%20the%20military%20to%20operate%20freely%20anywhere%20that%20has%20been%20declared%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisturbed%20area%26quot%3B%3B%20no%20military%20personnel%20in%20an%20area%20where%20AFSPA%20is%20in%20force%20can%20be%20prosecuted%20without%20the%20Centre's%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%2019%20police%20station%20areas%20in%20Manipur%20were%20not%20under%20AFSPA%20coverage%20as%20they%20were%20considered%20peaceful.%20The%20recent%20escalation%20in%20violence%2C%20however%2C%20has%20brought%20the%20controversial%20law%20back%20to%20at%20least%20six%20police%20station%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20areas%20where%20the%20security%20forces%20can%20operate%20under%20the%20immunity%20provided%20by%20AFSPA%20in%20Manipur%20are%20Sekmai%20and%20Lamsang%20in%20Imphal%20West%20district%2C%20Lamlai%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20Jiribam%20in%20Jiribam%20district%2C%20Leimakhong%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20Moirang%20in%20Bishnupur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFSPA%20was%20withdrawn%20from%2019%20police%20station%20areas%20in%20the%20valley%20region%20after%20seeing%20normalcy.%20The%20Meitei-Kuki%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20May%20202