s'%20insult%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20every%20Marathi%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20campaigning%20in%20Aurangabad%20ahead%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20on%20November%2020%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20vote%20Jihad%20has%20begun%20in%20the%20state%20now.%20We%20saw%20that%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20In%20Dhule%2C%20we%20were%20ahead%20by%201.90%20lakh%20votes%20but%20the%20Malegaon%20(assembly%20segment)%20had%201.94%20lakh%20votes%20and%20we%20were%20defeated%20by%20only%204%2C000%20votes.%20This%20vote%20Jihad%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20our%20defeat%20there%20because%20we%20were%20not%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20election%20will%20see%20Maharashtra's%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20coalition%20and%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20fight%20for%20288%20seats.%20Counting%20is%20scheduled%20for%20November%2023.%20The%202019%20polls%20saw%20the%20BJP%20with%20105%20seats%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20with%2056%2C%20and%20Congress%20securing%2044.%20The%20MVA%20alliance%20gained%20momentum%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20winning%2030%20out%20of%2048%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Mahayuti%20coalition%20claimed%2017%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731577320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fkpt3ueko_kanhaiya-kumar-devendra-fadnavis-_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkanhaiya-kumar-instagram-reels-remark-against-amruta-fadnavis-sparks-row-7017646%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Kanhaiya%20Kumar%20has%20sparked%20controversy%20with%20his%20remarks%20targeting%20Amruta%20Fadnavis%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkanhaiya-kumar-instagram-reels-remark-against-amruta-fadnav