0is%20expected%20to%20but%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20the%20fantasy%20epic%20seeks%20to%20ride%20on%20a%20blend%20of%20the%20actor's%20charisma%2C%20the%20thrills%20generated%20by%20the%20exploits%20of%20warriors%20of%20a%20distant%20past%20and%20the%20sweeping%20visual%20grandeur%20that%20cinematographer%20Vetri%20Palanisamy%20rustles%20up%2C%20%3Cem%3EKanguva%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebarely%20stays%20afloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FftcTEWWzhpk%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Kanguva%20(Hindi)%20-%20Release%20Trailer%20%7C%20Suriya%20%7C%20Bobby%20Deol%20%7C%20Siva%20%7C%20Devi%20Sri%20Prasad%20%7C%20Studio%20Green%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%2030%20minutes%20of%20the%20Tamil-language%20film%20written%20and%20directed%20by%20Siva%20is%20as%20brain-numbingly%20sloppy%20as%20any%20half-an-hour%20of%20cinema%20that%20we%20have%20ever%20seen.%20Be%20it%20the%20banal%20dialogue%2C%20the%20shrill%20pitching%20of%20the%20delivery%2C%20the%20perfunctory%20acting%20and%20the%20feeble%20stabs%20at%20humour%2C%20nothing%20is%20in%20order.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20stretch%20adds%20up%20to%20a%20wayward%20and%20mercifully%20quick%20lowdown%20on%20three%20present-day%20bounty%20hunters%20who%20help%20the%20police%20nab%20slippery%20law-breakers.%20One%20of%20them%20ends%20up%20dead%20on%20a%20boat%20in%20Goa%2C%20sending%20Francis%20Theodore%20(Suriya)%20and%20his%20voluble%2C%20doltish%20sidekick%20Colt%2095%20(Yogi%20Babu)%20scurrying%20for%20cover.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shoddy%20prelude%20takes%20the%20film%20nowhere%20and%20tells%20us%20next%20to%20nothing%20about%20the%20characters%20who%20romp%20about%20on%20the%20screen%20and%20yell%20at%20each%20other%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20voices.%20The%20shrillest%20of%20them%20all%20is%20Angela%20(Disha%20Patani)%2C%20Francis'%20girlfriend-turned-rival%20moneygrubber.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20only%20thing%20that%20emerges%20from%20the%20free-for-all%20is%20that%20Francis%20senses%20an%20unexplained%20connection%20with%20a%20runaway%20boy%20whose%20brain%20cells%20have%20been%20tampered%20with%20at%20a%20Russian%20biomedical%20laboratory%20before%20he%20escapes%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20the%20evil%20scientists%20and%20their%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColt%2095%20is%20meant%20to%20provide%20comic%20relief.%20Angela%20exists%20because%20the%20screenplay%20needs%20somebody%20who%20can%20inject%20meaningless%20romantic%20diversion%20into%20the%20proceedings.%20Neither%20of%20them%20serves%20the%20intended%20purpose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20opening%20minutes%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20rest%20the%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3EKanguva%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshows%20marked%20improvement%20(at%20last%20with%20regard%20to%20imagery%20and%20intensity)%20once%20it%20plunges%20into%20the%20past%20-%20the%20year%20is%201070%20AD%20and%20thereabouts%20-%20and%20follows%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20tribal%20inhabitants%20of%20five%20islands%20that%20are%20united%20by%20language%20but%20are%20violently%20at%20odds%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20each%20one%20of%20them%20represents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20male%20protagonist%20here%20is%20Kanguva%20(Suriya)%2C%20the%20prince%20and%20principal%20warrior%20of%20Perumaachi%20island.%20The%20Perumanathans%20are%20fire%20worshippers%20and%20their%20land%20is%20lust%20green.%20It%20is%20an%20island%20that%20is%20worth%20dying%20for.%20But%20death%20certainly%20isn't%20on%20the%20hero's%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaiting%20to%20pounce%20upon%20the%20islanders%20are%2025%2C000%20soldiers%20of%20a%20Roman%20army%20looking%20for%20a%20secluded%20zone%20for%20the%20training%20of%20their%20men.%20When%20all%20is%20about%20to%20be%20lost%20-%20these%20people%20seem%20to%20always%20hang%20by%20a%20thread%20as%20the%20Romans%2C%20traitors%20and%20enemies%20lying%20in%20wait%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Arathi%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20vice-like%20grip%20of%20Uthiran%20(Bobby%20Deol)%20-%20Konguva%20helps%20his%20people%20fight%20their%20way%20out%20of%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20that%20Kanguva%20needs%20any%20help%20from%20anybody.%20He%20is%20a%20force%20of%20nature%2C%20an%20unstoppable%20one-man%20army.%20And%20once%20he%20sets%20himself%20a%20goal%2C%20nobody%20and%20nothing%20can%20deflect%20him%20from%20his%20path.%20He%20likens%20himself%20to%20trees%20in%20a%20forest%20that%20aren't%20swayed%20by%20the%20winds%20and%20to%20streams%20that%20flow%20past%20the%20biggest%20rocks%20in%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20what%20he%20says%20about%20himself%20and%20how%20a%20God-like%20voiceover%20introduces%20him%20to%20the%20audience%20ahead%20of%20his%20grand%20entry%20scene%2C%20it%20is%20also%20background%20songs%20that%20provide%20elucidation%20on%20his%20inner%20thoughts.%20But%20do%20not%20let%20that%20fool%20you%2C%20the%20music%20in%20Kanguva%20is%20anything%20but%20subtle.%20It%20is%20at%20best%20a%20distraction%20that%20the%20film%20would%20have%20done%20well%20to%20dial%20down.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20film's%20sound%20design%20definitely%20needed%20much%20more%20thought%20and%20work%20as%20did%20the%20characterisation.%20None%20of%20the%20people%20we%20see%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20including%20Kanguva%2C%20is%20accorded%20any%20wriggle-room%20to%20shape%20themselves%20into%20rounded%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20sheer%20vigour%20that%20Suriya%20brings%20to%20bear%20upon%20the%20titular%20hero%2C%20it%20is%20surprising%20that%20the%20scriptwriters%20did%20not%20deem%20it%20necessary%20to%20inform%20the%20protagonist%20with%20more%20than%20just%20the%20broad%20contours%20that%20he%20is%20boxed%20into.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film's%20biggest%20missed%20opportunity%20pertains%20to%20the%20facet%20of%20the%20intrepid%20warrior%20that%20reflects%20a%20'maternal'%20nourisher%20when%20a%20desperate%20orphan%20boy%20cries%20out%20for%20help.%20The%20masculine%20in%20Kanguva%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20giving%20way%20to%20an%20individual%20who%20not%20only%20protects%20(by%20killing%20a%20crocodile%20with%20his%20bare%20hands%2C%20when%20necessary)%20but%20also%20'weans'%20a%20motherless%20boy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20significant%20aspect%20of%20the%20story%20is%20allowed%20to%20disappear%20into%20a%20miasma%20of%20avoidable%20cliches.%20That%20is%20because%20%3Cem%3EKanguva%20%3C%2Fem%3Eisn't%20looking%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20the%20familiar.%20It%20is%20intent%20on%20being%20the%20Tamil%20%3Cem%3EBaahubali%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EKGF%3C%2Fem%3E.%20And%20that%20is%20its%20undoing.%20The%20immense%20potential%20of%20the%20core%20idea%20of%20dealing%20with%20the%20past%20and%20present%20as%20a%20seamless%20continuum%20remains%20largely%20untapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20a%20bulk%20of%20the%20film%20plays%20out%20in%20the%20past%2C%20which%20probably%20is%20just%20as%20well.%20The%20portions%20that%20are%20set%20in%20the%20present%20are%20a%20disappointingly%20patchy%20pastiche%20of%20science%20fiction%2C%20all-out%20action%20movie%20heroics%20and%20emotional%20tugs%20at%20the%20heartstrings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20climax%20flits%20between%20the%20eleventh%20century%20and%202024.%20In%20both%2C%20the%20hero%20is%20engaged%20in%20a%20mission%20to%20defeat%20an%20adversary.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20bad%20guy%20in%20the%20past%20is%20a%20stodgy%20caricature%20rather%20than%20a%20truly%20menacing%20foe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBobby%20Deol%2C%20in%20his%20Tamil%20debut%2C%20is%20called%20upon%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20screen%20during%20the%20limited%20time%20that%20he%20has%20on%20it.%20But%20there%20is%20so%20much%20happening%20around%20him%20that%2C%20like%20much%20else%20in%20the%20film%2C%20he%20is%20left%20jostling%20for%20space%20and%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20Suriya%20in%20a%20dual%20role.%20The%20hoary%20avatar%20that%20he%20dons%20works%20infinitely%20better%20than%20the%20contemporary%20one.%20That%20reflects%20the%20film%20as%20a%20whole%3A%20%3Cem%3EKanguva%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20like%20two%20separate%20films%2C%20with%20the%20past%20weighing%20heavy%20on%20the%20present%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKanguva%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20visual%20treat%20enhanced%20by%20the%20star's%20tremendous%20screen%20presence.%20If%20only%20the%20script%20had%20more%20to%20it%20than%20just%20the%20sensory%20and%20the%20visceral%2C%20this%20would%20have%20been%20a%20film%20fully%20deserving%20of%20the%20sequel%20that%20is%20in%20the%20works.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKanguva%20%3C%2Fem%3Edrops%20more%20than%20a%20few%20hints%20of%20a%20follow-up.%20Should%20we%20be%20excited%3F%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20heading%20for%20a%20great%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20somebody%20says%20in%20the%20final%20moments%20of%20the%20film.%20Are%20we%3F%20Not%20if%20the%20writing%20is%20in%20the%20same%20vein.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731577020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frfeus4i_e_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkanguva-review-its-intent-on-being-the-tamil-baahubali-and-kgf-remains-untapped-2-5-stars-7017602%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kanguva%20is%20a%20visual%20treat%20enhanced%20by%20Suriya's%20tremendous%20screen%20presence%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rapido%20reports%202.5x%20increase%20in%20gross%20order%20value%20to%20Rs%202%2C461%20cr%20in%20Q2FY25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731576915000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww