aking%20runs%20or%20taking%20wickets%2C%20there%20will%20be%20conversations%20around%20that%20kind%20of%20a%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team%2C%20you%20get%20a%20slack%20for%20that%2C%20and%20if%20you%20are%20the%20world's%20best%20batter%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20-%20maybe%20longer%20-%20across%20formats%2C%20I%20think%20Virat%20may%20get%20a%20bit%20more%20slack%20than%20somebody%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20for%20this%20series'%20sake%2C%20Test%20cricket's%20sakes%2C%20they%20both%20come%20out%2C%20get%20back%20to%20their%20best%20form%20and%20score%20plenty%20of%20runs%20for%20India%2C%20but%20also%20Test%20cricket.%20We%20want%20to%20see%20the%20Australian%20attack%20which%20is%20a%20good%20one%2C%20take%20on%20the%20top-order%20batting%20of%20India%20which%20is%20pretty%20strong%20in%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli's%20recent%20statistics%20are%20far%20from%20encouraging.%20His%20struggles%20against%20spin%20have%20worsened%2C%20scoring%20only%20192%20runs%20in%2010%20innings%20across%20five%20Tests%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%2C%20averaging%20just%2021.33%2C%20with%20one%20fifty%20and%20a%20best%20score%20of%2070.%20His%20scores%20in%20the%20recent%20home%20season%20were%3A%206%2C%2017%2C%2047%2C%2029*%2C%200%2C%2070%2C%201%2C%2017%2C%204%2C%20and%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Kohli%20has%20accumulated%20just%20250%20runs%20in%2012%20Test%20innings%20across%20six%20matches%2C%20averaging%2022.72%2C%20with%20one%20half-century%20and%20a%20top%20score%20of%2070.%20However%2C%20he%20has%20shown%20better%20form%20in%20away%20tours%20to%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20scoring%20561%20runs%20in%20the%20ongoing%20WTC%20cycle%202023-25%2C%20with%20a%20century%2C%20three%20fifties%2C%20and%20a%20best%20score%20of%20121%20across%20nine%20Tests%20and%2016%20innings%2C%20averaging%2037.40.