pany%20announced%20a%2010%25%20reduction%20in%20positions%20last%20month%2C%20equivalent%20to%20about%2017%2C000%20employees.%20The%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20restoring%20Boeing's%20competitive%20edge%20as%20it%20reels%20from%20multiple%20crises%2C%20including%20reduced%20output%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20near-catastrophic%20accident%20in%20January%20and%20a%20strike%20that%20shut%20down%20most%20of%20its%20production%20for%20seven%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20Boeing%20cuts%20too%20deep%20or%20in%20the%20wrong%20places%2C%20it%20risks%20undermining%20its%20eventual%20recovery%20from%20years%20of%20turmoil.%20Manufacturers%20like%20Boeing%20used%20to%20count%20on%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20furloughed%20workers%20to%20eventually%20return%20to%20work.%20That%20pattern%20was%20broken%20when%20its%20Covid-era%20layoffs%20spurred%20a%20permanent%20exodus%2C%20including%20top-flight%20engineers%20and%20mechanics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20these%20days%2C%20workers%20have%20more%20options.%20Unemployment%20in%20Seattle%20is%20hovering%20at%204%25%20and%20aerospace%20workers%20are%20in%20high%20demand%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20region's%20booming%20space%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERivals%20like%20SpaceX%2C%20Blue%20Origin%20LLC%20and%20Amazon.com%20Inc.'s%20Project%20Kuiper%20are%20all%20searching%20for%20new%20hires%20to%20support%20rapidly%20growing%20operations%20around%20Seattle%2C%20where%20Boeing%20manufactures%20most%20of%20its%20commercial%20airplanes%2C%20said%20Stan%20Shull%2C%20a%20space%20industry%20analyst%20and%20consultant%20at%20Alliance%20Velocity%20LLC.%20The%20opportunities%20range%20from%20working%20on%20Starlink%20satellites%20for%20Elon%20Musk's%20space%20venture%20to%20helping%20with%20rockets%2C%20space%20stations%2C%20lunar%20landers%20and%20the%20like%20for%20Jeff%20Bezos's%20rival%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETight%20Market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20about%201%2C350%20job%20openings%20at%20more%20than%2050%20space%20companies%20in%20the%20Puget%20Sound%20region%2C%20by%20Shull's%20count.%20While%20engineers%20of%20all%20stripes%20are%20in%20demand%2C%20the%20companies%20are%20also%20searching%20for%20machinists%2C%20administrative%20help%2C%20sales%20and%20marketing%20staff%20and%20other%20positions%2C%20said%20Shull.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShifting%20demographics%20within%20the%20US%20workforce%20and%20continued%20low%20unemployment%20mean%20Boeing%20will%20face%20more%20competition%20when%20it%20needs%20to%20resume%20hiring%20to%20support%20its%20growth%2C%20said%20Richard%20Aboulafia%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20with%20AeroDynamic%20Advisory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20works%20fine%20as%20long%20as%20labor%20markets%20aren't%20tight%2C%26quot%3B%20Aboulafia%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BBut%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20labor%20markets%20are%20really%20tight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20rolling%20out%20blanket%20workforce%20cuts%20are%20%26quot%3Bthe%20surest%20formula%20for%20losing%2010%25%20of%20your%20best%20people%26quot%3B%20who%20will%20gravitate%20to%20potentially%20more%20stable%20employers%2C%20Aboulafia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lost%20institutional%20knowledge%20was%20apparent%20as%20the%20company%20made%20only%20halting%20progress%20ramping%20up%20manufacturing%20of%20its%20737%20Max%20jetliner%20this%20decade.%20Executives%20later%20acknowledged%20they'd%20underestimated%20the%20training%20required%20to%20bring%20the%20large%20influx%20of%20new%20hires%20up%20to%20speed%20in%20their%20factories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Reset%20Priorities'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20company%20is%20staffed%20for%20peak%20production%20levels%20it%20likely%20won't%20see%20for%20years%2C%20especially%20after%20a%2053-day%20strike%20largely%20halted%20work%20in%20its%20plants%20across%20the%20west%20coast.%20Boeing%20had%20171%2C000%20employees%20at%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%2C%2012%25%20more%20than%20the%20153%2C000%20it%20employed%20five%20years%20earlier%2C%20when%20its%20factories%20were%20at%20their%20pre-crisis%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20workers%20and%20Boeing%20hit%20a%20low%20during%20the%20strike%20that%20just%20ended.%20Boeing%20was%20finally%20able%20to%20settle%20the%20dispute%20with%20concessions%20including%20a%2038%25%20wage%20improvement%2C%20but%20many%20employees%20remain%20antagonized%20by%20a%20company%20they%20say%20has%20not%20paid%20them%20fairly%20for%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKelly%20Ortberg%2C%20who%20was%20hired%20in%20August%20as%20chief%20executive%20officer%20to%20turn%20around%20Boeing%2C%20has%20said%20the%2010%25%20workforce%20reduction%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20campaign%20to%20cut%20out%20bloat%20and%20inefficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20reset%20priorities%20and%20create%20a%20leaner%2C%20more%20focused%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20Ortberg%20said%20during%20an%20Oct.%2023%20earnings%20call.%20The%20cuts%20are%20intended%20to%20%26quot%3Bfocus%20on%20consolidation%20of%20areas%20where%20we're%20not%20efficient%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20continue%20to%20focus%20on%20reducing%20non-essential%20activity.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731576120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ftrerrijg_boeing-job-cuts-layoffs_625x300_12_October_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboeing-to-fire-10-workforce-17-000-employees-set-to-be-sacked-7017481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing%20Co.%20will%20start%20sending%20out%20pink%20slips%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20employees%20affected%20by%20a%20planned%20round%20of%20job%20cuts%2C%20a%20delicate%20balancing%20act%20between%20improvin