ttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20village%20was%20under%20the%20Nizam%20of%20Hyderabad...%20when%20India%20was%20under%20the%20British.%20There%20was%20a%20fire...%20this%20was%20when%20Hindus%20were%20being%20selectively%20killed.%20And%2C%20in%20this%20fire%2C%20his%20home%20was%20also%20burned%20down%2C%20in%20which%20his%20mother%20and%20family%20were%20killed.%20But%20Khargeji%20does%20not%20say%20this...%20because%20he%20knows%20if%20he%20says%20it%2C%20then%20Muslim%20votes%20will%20shift.%20He%20forgot%20the%20sacrifice%20of%20his%20family%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Kharge's%20son%20Priyank%20said%20his%20father%20narrowly%20escaped%20death%20during%20that%20tragic%20incident%20and%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%209-time%20MLA%2C%20an%20MP%2C%20a%20Union%20Minister%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20a%20Congress%20president.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20tragedy%2C%20he%20never%20exploited%20it%20for%20political%20gain%2C%20never%20played%20the%20victim%20card%20and%20never%20let%20hatred%20define%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20minister%20said%20the%20atrocities%20against%20the%20Kharge%20family%20was%20committed%20by%20Razakars%2C%20not%20the%20entire%20Muslim%20community.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20community%20has%20bad%20apples%20and%20individuals%20who%20do%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyank%20Kharge%20said%20the%2082-year-old%20Congress%20chief%20is%20fighting%20tirelessly%20to%20uphold%20the%20values%20of%20Buddha-Basavanna-Ambedkar%20and%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20Yogi%20Ji%2C%20take%20your%20hate%20elsewhere.%20You%20cannot%20bulldoze%20his%20principles%20or%20his%20ideology.%20Try%20winning%20the%20elections%20on%20PM%C2%A0%40narendramodi%20ji's%20'achievements'%20instead%20trying%20to%20sow%20seeds%20of%20hatred%20in%20the%20society%20for%20political%20gains%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20had%20launched%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20leader%20over%20his%20%26quot%3Bbatenge%20to%20katenge%26quot%3B%20remarks%20that%20the%20Opposition%20has%20described%20as%20divisive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20(political)%20leaders%20live%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20sadhus%20and%20become%20politicians...%20some%20even%20become%20chief%20ministers.%20They%20wear%20gerua%20(saffron)%20clothes%20and%20have%20no%20hair%20on%20their%20heads...%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20chief%20said%2C%20clearly%20referring%20to%20Mr%20Adityanath.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say...%20either%20wear%20white%20clothes%20or%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20sanyasi%2C%20get%20out%20of%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20one%20hand%20you%20wear%20gerua%20clothes...%20on%20the%20other%20you%20say%20'batenge%20toh%20katenge'.%20They%20are%20spreading%20hatred%20among%20the%20people%20and%20are%20trying%20to%20divide%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731575280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F0d1bfokg_priyank-kharge-yogi-split_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-yogi-adityanath-priyank-kharge-take-hate-elsewhere-m-kharges-son-on-yogi-adityanaths-razakar-barb-7017351%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20barbs%20at%20his%20father%20and%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Karnataka%20Minister%20Priyank%20Kharge%20has%20said%20the%20veteran%20leader%20never%20exploited%20personal%20tragedy%20for%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20gain%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2