0veteran%20and%20one-time%20Democratic%20White%20House%20contender%2C%20Gabbard%20brings%20the%20%26quot%3Bfearless%20spirit%20that%20has%20defined%20her%20illustrious%20career%20to%20our%20intelligence%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGabbard%2C%20who%20earlier%20opposed%20US%20support%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20thanked%20the%20President-elect%20for%20the%20opportunity%2C%20adding%20she%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20getting%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Gabbard%20all%20set%20to%20succeed%20Avril%20Haines%20as%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%2C%20here%20are%20five%20facts%20about%20her%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Early%20Life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETulsi%20Gabbard%20was%20born%20on%20April%2012%2C%201981%2C%20in%20Leloaloa%2C%20American%20Samoa.%20When%20she%20was%20two%20years%20old%2C%20her%20family%20settled%20in%20Hawaii.%20As%20a%20teenager%2C%20she%20co-founded%20the%20Healthy%20Hawai'i%20Coalition%2C%20an%20environmental%20non-profit.%20She%20completed%20a%20B.S.B.A.%20in%20Business%20Administration%20from%20the%20Hawaii%20Pacific%20University%20in%202009.%20Her%20father%2C%20Mike%20Gabbard%2C%20switched%20from%20the%20Republican%20Party%20to%20Democrats%20and%20is%20a%20Hawaii%20State%20Senator.%20She%20is%20married%20to%20Abraham%20Williams%2C%20a%20cinematographer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Military%20Service%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGabbard%20has%20served%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20in%20the%20Army%20National%20Guard.%20She%20was%20deployed%20to%20Iraq%20and%20Kuwait.%20In%202005%2C%20she%20was%20honoured%20with%20a%20Combat%20Medical%20Badge%20for%20%26quot%3Bparticipation%20in%20combat%20operations%20under%20enemy%20hostile%20fire%20in%20support%20of%20Operation%20Iraqi%20Freedom%20III%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20Hawaii%20National%20Guard.%20Although%20Gabbard%20has%20not%20held%20any%20senior%20government%20roles%20unlike%20past%20directors%2C%20she%20has%20two%20years%20of%20experience%20on%20the%20House%20Homeland%20Security%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20First%20Hindu%20elected%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGabbard%20was%20elected%20to%20Hawaii's%20House%20of%20Representatives%20at%2021%20but%20had%20to%20leave%20after%20a%20single%20term%20following%20her%20National%20Guard%20unit's%20deployment%20to%20Iraq.%20Later%2C%20she%20was%20elected%20to%20Congress%20where%20she%20represented%20Hawaii.%20She%20became%20the%20first%20Hindu%20member%20of%20the%20House%20and%20was%20sworn%20into%20office%20with%20her%20hand%20on%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita.%20She%20was%20also%20the%20first%20American%20Samoan%20elected%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Presidential%20aspirations%20and%20party%20exit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Gabbard%20came%20into%20the%20spotlight%2C%20seeking%20the%20Democratic%20nomination%20for%20the%20President.%20She%20opposed%20the%20country's%20involvement%20in%20foreign%20military%20conflicts.%20She%20later%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20race%20and%20endorsed%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20eventually%20won%20the%20election.%20After%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20she%20left%20the%20Democratic%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Trump%20campaign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Gabbard%20extended%20support%20to%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20receiving%20popularity%20among%20his%20supporters.%20At%20a%20rally%20in%20North%20Carolina%20in%20October%2C%20she%20officially%20announced%20becoming%20a%20Republican%20and%20termed%20the%20current%20Democratic%20Party%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unrecognisable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731573900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Fnhd39014_tulsi-gabbard_625x300_19_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-names-tulsi-gabbard-as-director-of-nation