A%22%3Cp%3EChaotic%20scenes%20played%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Prayagraj%20this%20morning%20as%20students%20protesting%20outside%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20office%20clashed%20with%20police%20and%20broke%20through%20barricades.%20The%20students%20are%20demanding%20that%20exams%20for%20recruitment%20to%20Provincial%20Civil%20Service%20(PCS)%20and%20Review%20and%20Assistant%20Review%20Officer%20posts%20be%20held%20in%20a%20single%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20service%20body%20had%20earlier%20announced%20that%20the%20PCS%20(prelims)%20will%20be%20held%20on%20December%207%20and%208%20in%20two%20shifts%20--%209.30%20am%20to%2011.30%20am%20and%202.30%20pm%20to%204.30%20pm.%20The%20RO%2FARO%20exam%20was%20scheduled%20for%20December%2022%20and%2023%2C%20also%20in%20two%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20are%20demanding%20%26quot%3Bone%20day%2C%20one%20shift%26quot%3B%20exams%20as%20they%20fear%20multiple%20exam%20dates%20and%20shifts%20will%20raise%20the%20risk%20of%20paper%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20has%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20hold%20exams%20in%20shifts%20as%20been%20taken%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20applicants%20and%20to%20uphold%20the%20exam's%20sanctity.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20commission%20said%20they%20would%20hold%20exams%20exclusively%20at%20centres%20where%20possibility%20of%20irregularities%20is%20eliminated.%20The%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20only%20government%20or%20funded%20educational%20institutions%20within%2010-km%20radius%20of%20a%20bus%20stand%2C%20railway%20station%20or%20treasury%2C%20and%20with%20no%20history%20of%20suspicion%20or%20blacklisting%20are%20being%20designated%20as%20examination%20centres.%20It%20is%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20the%20commission%20had%20to%20opt%20for%20exams%20in%20shifts%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20has%20said%20a%20normalisation%20process%20will%20be%20used%20to%20evaluate%20the%20results%20because%20the%20exams%20are%20being%20held%20across%20multiple%20days%20or%20shifts.%20This%2C%20the%20panel%20said%2C%20is%20commonly%20used%20across%20the%20country%20and%20is%20supported%20by%20several%20court%20rulings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20are%20not%20convinced.%20Vimal%20Tripathi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20protesters%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20commission%20says%20it%20can%20conduct%20these%20exams%20only%20at%20government%20schools%20in%2041%20districts%20because%20it%20has%20limited%20number%20of%20centres.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20commission%20has%20only%20one%20responsibility%20and%20it%20has%20failed%20in%20that%20as%20well.%20Why%20can't%20the%20exams%20be%20held%20in%20a%20single%20day%20across%20all%20the%20districts%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20protests%20swell%2C%20authorities%20in%20the%20public%20service%20commission%20are%20now%20meeting%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20meeting%20may%20end%20in%20a%20relief%20to%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%2012%20people%20after%20vandalism%20at%20the%20commission's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20Abhishek%20Bharti%20said%20some%20%26quot%3Banti-social%20elements%26quot%3B%20had%20infiltrated%20the%20protesters%20and%20were%20provoking%20them.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20detained%20them%20and%20are%20taking%20action.%20We%20have%20not%20taken%20any%20woman%20student%20in%20custody.%20This%20is%20a%20fake%20news%20being%20circulated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20have%20sparked%20a%20political%20row%2C%20with%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20targeting%20the%20state%20government.%20Slamming%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20was%20the%20agitation%20was%20%26quot%3Byogi%20vs.%20competitor%20students%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20if%20the%20government%20would%20now%20use%20bulldozers%20to%20target%20student%20accommodations.%20%26quot%3BThe%20rise%20of%20the%20students%20will%20be%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20has%20called%20for%20an%20amicable%20solution.%20The%20BJP%20government%2C%20it%20has%20said%2C%20has%20set%20an%20example%20of%20fair%20recruitment%20by%20taking%20action%20against%20%26quot%3Brecruitment%20mafia%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAll%20competent%20officials%20should%20listen%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20students%20sensitively%20and%20find%20a%20quick%20solution.%20Ensure%20that%20the%20precious%20time%20of%20the%20students%20is%20not%20spent%20in%20agitation%20but%20in%20their%20preparation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731567960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fbc0a6it_prayagraj_625x300_14_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprayagraj-students-protest-job-exams-schedule-officials-look-for-way-out-7016411%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chaotic%20scenes%20played%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Prayagraj%20this%20morning%20as%20students%20protesting%20outside%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20office%20clashed%20with%20police%20and%20broke%20through%20barricades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprayagraj-students-protest-job-exams-schedule-officials-look-for-way-out-7016411%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paul%20tries%20to%20goad%20Tyson%20at%20baffling%20news%20conference%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731566738000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_sport%2F7cca%2Flive%2F42884ae0-a226-11ef-9ad6-c5b69b233c3a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2