aired.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-jpg.avif%202970w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-300x161.avif%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-500x268.avif%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-768x412.avif%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-1536x823.avif%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-2048x1098.avif%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-1200x643.avif%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FPerception-AI-1_11zon-1731320432-150x80.avif%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-378561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPerception.ai%20Private%20Limited%20is%20leveraging%20generative%20AI%20to%20digitally%20empower%20the%20visually%20impaired.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20often-overlooked%20realm%20of%20mental%20health%2C%20%E2%80%98Raahee%E2%80%99%20is%20making%20significant%20strides%20in%20providing%20accessible%20support%20and%20therapy.%20Through%20its%20empathetic%20and%20humanist%20approach%2C%20Raahee%E2%80%99s%20platform%20offers%20an%20application%20and%20website%20that%20connect%20users%20with%20therapists%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20With%20over%201%2C000%20users%20already%20benefiting%20from%20their%20services%2C%20Raahee%20is%20advancing%20the%20crucial%20social%20cause%20of%20making%20mental%20healthcare%20affordable%20and%20dismantling%20its%20associated%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20thingQbator%20programme%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98thingQbator%E2%80%99%20began%20in%202018%20as%20a%20maker%20space%20for%20Cisco%E2%80%99s%20engineers%20to%20don%20their%20innovation%20caps%20and%20transform%20their%20ideas%20into%20working%20prototypes.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20internal%20incubator%20prompted%20the%20company%20to%20scale%20it%20up%20in%20partnership%20with%20nasscom%20foundation%20and%20open%20it%20to%20universities%20across%20the%20country%20to%20promote%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20encompasses%20a%20four-stage%20programme%2C%20nurturing%20the%20transformation%20of%20ideas%20into%20thriving%20ventures.%20From%20the%20ideation%20stage%20to%20incubation%2C%20the%20top%2010%20teams%20are%20granted%20a%20seed%20fund%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20marking%20the%20transition%20of%20their%20social%20ventures%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seventh%20edition%20of%20thingQbator%20is%20currently%20underway%2C%20mentoring%20and%20nurturing%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20students%20with%20a%20vision%20aligned%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20incubating%20new%20startups%2C%20thingQbator%20also%20offers%20a%20myriad%20of%20learning%20opportunities%20for%20students%20across%20the%20country.%20This%20learning%20platform%20offers%20over%2018%20courses%20in%20hardware%20and%20software%20that%20students%20can%20complete%20at%20their%20convenience%20to%20enhance%20their%20technical%20skills.%20This%20platform%20is%20available%20to%20all%20students%20who%20register.%20The%20courses%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20from%20building%20apps%20using%20Flutter%20to%20creating%20websites%2C%20web%20development%20skills%2C%20and%20working%20with%20Raspberry%20Pi%203%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20a%20high%20level%20of%20technical%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2030%2C000%20course%20completion%20certificates%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20and%20over%2016%2C000%20unique%20students%20have%20received%20course%20completion%20certificates%20as%20of%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20a%20platform%20that%20transcends%20entrepreneurial%20incubation%2C%20thingQbator%20is%20empowering%20young%20Indians%20to%20become%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20technology%20and%20innovation.%20This%20initiative%20serves%20as%20a%20powerful%20catalyst%2C%20propelling%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20technologically%20advanced%20and%20socially%20empowered%20India%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20truly%20believe%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20ignite%20the%20imaginations%20of%20young%20minds%2C%20and%20universities%20and%20other%20educational%20institutions%20are%20the%20ideal%20environments%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20explore%20new%20ideas.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20aim%20to%20do%20through%20our%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20we%20collaborate%20with%20universities%20to%20identify%20and%20mentor%20young%20minds%2C%20helping%20them%20shape%20and%20realize%20their%20entrepreneurial%20aspirations.%20This%20initiative%20is%20not%20just%20about%20nurturing%20startups%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20empowering%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20innovators%20to%20create%20impactful%20solutions%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Harish%20Krishnan%2C%20Managing%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20Chief%20Policy%20Officer%2C%20Cisco%20India%20%26amp%3B%20SAARC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20%26amp%3B%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20nasscom%20foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731321261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D378406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Cisco%20and%20nasscom%20foundation%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20nurtures%20young%20innovators%20