0the%20creation%20of%2050%20episodes%20of%20%3Cem%3EMehfil-e-Rajasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20around%20110%20artists.%20Some%20of%20these%20episodes%20are%20now%20available%20on%20Spotify%2C%20bringing%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20music%20to%20a%20broader%20audience.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20just%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20catalyst%3B%20I%20connected%20the%20dots%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20experience%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music%20live%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20unmistakable%20moment%20when%20your%20ears%20immediately%20perk%20up.%20This%20art%20form%20has%20been%20perfected%20over%20generations%2C%20so%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20tradition%20that%20it%20resonates%20through%20your%20very%20bones.%20It%20feels%20as%20if%20the%20artists%2C%20singing%20with%20heads%20held%20high%2C%20are%20not%20performing%20for%20the%20audience%2C%20but%20singing%20directly%20to%20a%20higher%20power%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20only%20took%20one%20Shri%20Ravi%20Shankar%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20extend%20the%20sitar%E2%80%99s%20influence%20for%20another%20century.%20Similarly%2C%20it%20will%20only%20take%20a%20few%20properly%20trained%20and%20passionate%20young%20people%20to%20revive%20the%20rich%20music%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20ensure%20its%20survival%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20assures%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731072652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8733_11zon-1731069402.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D375518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20world%20where%20traditional%20art%20forms%20are%20fading%20away%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%20are%20on%20a%20missio