-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKalpit%20Veerwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20success%20stories%20of%20JEE%20Mains.%20The%20first%20student%20to%20ever%20score%20a%20perfect%20360%2F360%20in%20the%20exam%2C%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20not%20only%20earned%20him%20the%20All%20India%20Rank%201%20(AIR%201)%20in%20JEE%20Mains%202017%2C%20but%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20a%20remarkable%20career.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20computer%20science%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%20in%202021%2C%20Kalpit%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20investor%2C%20leading%20his%20successful%20startup%20AcadBoost%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20online%20education%2C%20software%2C%20and%20email%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20entrepreneurial%20ventures%2C%20Kalpit%20is%20an%20active%20mentor%20and%20advisor%20to%20several%20startups%2C%20helping%20students%20and%20young%20professionals%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332971%2Fbrillio-national-stem-learning-challenge-government-schools-rural-india-science-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducational%20and%20career%20pursuits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Through%20his%20platform%2C%20he%20also%20shares%20valuable%20content%20on%20exam%20preparation%2C%20business%20growth%2C%20and%20career-building%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEssential%20advice%20for%20JEE%20aspirants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20practical%20and%20insightful%20tips%20from%20Kalpit%20Veerwal%20that%20he%20believes%20are%20essential%20for%20cracking%20the%20JEE%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Build%20consistency%20in%20study%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%E2%80%99d%20give%20is%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20your%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kalpit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20He%20stresses%20that%20consistent%20study%20is%20more%20effective%20than%20short%2C%20intense%20bursts%20of%20effort.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20students%20who%20study%20regularly%2C%20even%20for%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20tend%20to%20outperform%20those%20who%20alternate%20between%20intense%20study%20sessions%20and%20periods%20of%20inactivity.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20sticking%20to%20a%20daily%20routine%20to%20steadily%20build%20your%20knowledge%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Focus%20on%20problem-solving%20over%20theory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpit%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9CReading%20theory%20is%20important%2C%20but%20practice%20makes%20perfect.%20The%20exam%20is%20all%20about%20solving%20problems.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20the%20JEE%20is%20a%20test%20of%20application%20rather%20than%20knowledge%2C%20he%20recommends%20solving%20as%20many%20problems%20as%20possible%20to%20deeply%20understand%20the%20concepts%20and%20sharpen%20your%20ability%20to%20tackle%20a%20variety%20of%20questions%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Revise%20frequently%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20chapter%20must%20be%20revised%20at%20least%20five%20to%20six%20times%20before%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalpit.%20He%20believes%20that%20regular%20revision%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20habits%20for%20any%20top%20scorer.%20Revisiting%20each%20chapter%20several%20times%20throughout%20the%20year%20helps%20reinforce%20your%20memory%20and%20solidify%20understanding.%20Kalpit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20revised%20chapters%20multiple%20times%20to%20ensure%20nothing%20was%20left%20to%20chance%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20students%20should%20also%20do%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Develop%20and%20practise%20a%20clear%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpit%20suggests%20that%20students%20should%20develop%20their%20exam%20strategy%20well%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20big%20day.%20%E2%80%9CSolve%20plenty%20of%20test%20papers%20at%20home%2C%20at%20your%20own%20pace%2C%20and%20identify%20which%20subjects%20come%20more%20naturally%20to%20you.%20This%20will%20help%20you%20decide%20which%20ones%20to%20tackle%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20know%20how%20much%20time%20to%20allocate%20to%20each%20section%2C%20when%20to%20skip%20difficult%20questions%2C%20and%20how%20to%20adapt%20your%20approach%20based%20on%20the%20difficulty%20level%20of%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728-300x297.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728-150x149.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-375474