unt%20Ama%20Haji%20would%20get%20her%20fill%20of%20%3Cem%3EYarkhandi%20pulao%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20her%20essay%2C%20Fida%20writes%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EYarkandi%20polla%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereflects%20the%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20Ladakh%20as%20a%20confluence%20of%20cultures.%20%E2%80%9CMade%20the%20traditional%20way%20%E2%80%94%20slow-cooked%20in%20a%20heavy%20stone%20pot%20called%20a%20%3Cem%3Edoltok%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20%3Cem%3ELadakhi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20dish%20was%20said%20to%20be%20symbolic%20of%20the%20big%20hearts%20(read%3A%20deep%20pockets)%20of%20the%20hosts%20for%20their%20guests.%20This%20bounty%20was%20proven%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20fat%2Fghee%20dripping%20down%20one%E2%80%99s%20elbows%20while%20eating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFun%20fact%3A%20Ladakh%20was%20a%20stranger%20to%20rice%2C%20the%20protagonist%20of%20the%20dish%2C%20until%20about%20seven%20decades%20ago.%20It%20was%20improved%20transport%20links%20and%20connectivity%20that%20transformed%20the%20once%20luxury%20item%20into%20a%20staple%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282445%2Findia-in-pics-ten-local-ladakhi-dish-history-culture-kunzes-angmo-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Ladakhi%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203147px)%20100vw%2C%203147px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3367-1730813982.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223147%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tarana%20Husain%20Khan%20interacted%20with%20a%20number%20of%20culinary%20virtuosos%20to%20understand%20the%20history%20behind%20South%20Asian%20cuisine%20and%20its%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20current%20gastronomic%20landscape%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3367-1730813982.jpg%203147w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl